{"updated_at": "2011-06-16T18:44:42Z", "repo": "rails", "created_at": "2011-06-16T18:44:15Z", "owner": "rails", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/1383327", "id": 1383327, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/1458", "issue_id": 1458, "user": {"repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jhtwong/repos", "type": "User", "html_url": "https://github.com/jhtwong", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jhtwong/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jhtwong/subscriptions", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jhtwong/following{/other_user}", "gravatar_id": "cbac8261deee7dc43c44e2fd62af9c14", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jhtwong/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jhtwong", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jhtwong/gists{/gist_id}", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/cbac8261deee7dc43c44e2fd62af9c14?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F1916dd4db010a27d419d07a8c838edb2.png", "id": 826393, "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jhtwong/events{/privacy}", "login": "jhtwong", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jhtwong/received_events", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jhtwong/followers"}, "body": "I like your idea of being more explicit. How about this:\r\nhttps://gist.github.com/1029924\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\n  def all(&block)\r\n    @railties_plus_engines ||= railties + engines\r\n    @railties_plus_engines.each(&block) if block\r\n    # Only after the block has been run against the railties and engines in the application\r\n    # will we call super with the block (which has the effect of running the block against the plugins in the\r\n    # application and returning the array of plugins)\r\n    @railties_plus_engines + super(&block)\r\n  end\r\n```", "_id": {"$oid": "5238510bbd3543c151011738"}, "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/1458#issuecomment-1383327"}
